    "name": "The Fabric of the Mind",
    "steam_appid": 2294430,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294430/extras/07e4fe77ce87d72c4e33686b0cf7dc99.webp?t=1770069793\" width=784 height=54 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294430/extras/8d5a09475d64d367f2ae0dde375a8a5d.poster.avif?t=1770069793\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294430/extras/8d5a09475d64d367f2ae0dde375a8a5d.webm?t=1770069793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294430/extras/8d5a09475d64d367f2ae0dde375a8a5d.mp4?t=1770069793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Fabric of the Mind</i> is an atmospheric platformer where movement is more than a tool - it's how you survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You don't just run and jump... You walk on walls, cling to ceilings and approach every room from any angle you want.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a strange, interconnected world filled with puzzles and hostile entities that react to your presence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master fluid movement, solve clever environmental challenges and uncover the unsettling fragments of a story and reveals your purpose in this world, as well as your final goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294430/extras/31e36a354be44a1ed42e0e507c38a29c.webp?t=1770069793\" width=514 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294430/extras/6d2eabd6ce25154ad20390fe7b37bfaf.poster.avif?t=1770069793\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294430/extras/6d2eabd6ce25154ad20390fe7b37bfaf.webm?t=1770069793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294430/extras/6d2eabd6ce25154ad20390fe7b37bfaf.mp4?t=1770069793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movement is the foundation of everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Walls, ceilings and corners are all part of the path forward. Wall jumps, double jump and gravity-defying traversal chain together to create a smooth, flowing movement system that rewards precision and creativity. Rooms are built to be approached from multiple angles, so there is never only a single &quot;correct&quot; way through.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles are woven directly into the environment. Redirect energy, manipulate systems and open new paths. These mechanics are taught and explained with clever and intuitive level design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some threats can be avoided, others have to outrun. Tension comes from timing, positioning and momentun. Constant movement and awareness is key.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294430/extras/ef6118250c0f5860ba577c2f542e1308.webp?t=1770069793\" width=757 height=54 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294430/extras/ab9b904dcc8939a6d5272d243f4bb848.poster.avif?t=1770069793\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294430/extras/ab9b904dcc8939a6d5272d243f4bb848.webm?t=1770069793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294430/extras/ab9b904dcc8939a6d5272d243f4bb848.mp4?t=1770069793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world is quiet, dark and interconnected.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scattered throughout the world are <i>Memory Cores</i>, remnants of something that was meant to be sealed away. Piecing them together reveals a chronological timeline of everything that has happened... and your role in it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294430/extras/0d6c9e976b86bdb92197c733448b9070.webp?t=1770069793\" width=572 height=54 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a dark, forgotten place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are alone, driven only by something you don't understand. A purpose, an instinct, a final goal. The environment is hostile, oppressive and unwelcoming, yet it carries the weight of immense pain and history.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You don't know why you're here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But something insists that you keep moving on...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294430/extras/9cdc0b1afe34f72fdbc75f9173e54433.webp?t=1770069793\" width=464 height=60 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fluent and challenging gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Very simple controls for keyboard and controller.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three different difficulty options, that can be changed at anytime.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Calmer puzzle sections.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An optional dark story to uncover.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An interconnected, non-linear world to discover.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14 unique areas with new and exciting enemies, mechanics and characters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A simple and readable monochrome artstyle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A brilliant original soundtrack.</p></li></ul>",
